{"tid":129603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"出咗身嘅 你哋見唔見到香港有希望？","createTime":"2017-02-21T17:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T18:59:53.000Z","uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"980c006531240fa1dd6f478bbc3ba6eb1cf3d531","tid":129603,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:10:35.000Z","msg":"就grad 日日諗將來<br />\n除咗發生沙士/股災 唔喺都都冇咩可能買到樓<br />\n日日返工 唔開心 點解你哋仲捱到 有希望咩？<br />\n定喺返工冇想像中咁慘？ OT喺佔多數？ 多唔多俾上司屌？<br />\n我返緊同返過嘅工 上司同事都好好 唔知出面大多數喺點<br />\n但如果真喺咁絕望 我真心唔想再行落去 可能搵幾年錢 行一轉地球 之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一喺就寄望移到民 起碼都有得住有得食 唔駛50 60歲仲要愁2餐1宿 如果得嘅話<br />\n你哋其實點睇？同埋喺搵工方面 grad個hon 2nd up同2nd low 有冇大分別 我marginal case 差少少 但又追唔到上去咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企冇公屋冇樓 父母5x歲 佢哋都諗住靠我<br />\n求大家俾下意見 真喺好心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf790c7acc33d749c93d1d910cef332a6a13d378","tid":129603,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:51:40.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665a825211b86bb73255ad4cb415ad781ec67d73","tid":129603,"uid":50193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T17:56:07.000Z","msg":"你喺咪做IT狗？"},{"pid":"e006148f8d5077404a78b49fcd3696d23cf2f554","tid":129603,"uid":49145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:00:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你喺咪做IT狗？</blockquote><br />\n搵到grad job 做it dog 不過會睇下點先 唔得嘅應該會轉行<br />\n識真it dog 佢要凌晨on call 如果喺咁 我應該一定轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全喺泯滅人權 咁樣仲駛安心瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be21e248f4f3e77813846f1ae19046d4b2ce37c4","tid":129603,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"出生了很久，覺得沒有<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\